errors.prescription:
1. Add a null check: if ($variable !== null) { $variable->{member}(); }
2. Use the nullsafe operator (PHP 8.0+): $variable?->{member}();
3. Narrow the type with instanceof: if ($variable instanceof ClassName) { ... }
4. Fix the source to never return null if null is not a valid state.

